iv class=\"inner content-bg\">\n\n<div class=\"column\" id=\"recruit-kyouiku\">\n<div class=\"column-inner\">\n<div class=\"article\">\n<p class=\"entry-title\">安全運転講習</p>\n<p class=\"figure right\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-903\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.iwate-kenpokubus.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/kenpokubus/images/recruit/kyouiku_01.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"165\" /></p>\n<ul>\n<li>運転士の心構え</li>\n<li>運転士安全服務規定</li>\n<li>点呼執行規定</li>\n<li>自動車運輸安全管理規定</li>\n<li>安全運行指導協議会</li>\n<li>危険予知トレーニング</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"article\">\n<p class=\"entry-title\">車両機器講習</p>\n<p class=\"figure right\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-903\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.iwate-kenpokubus.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/kenpokubus/images/recruit/kyouiku_02.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"165\" /><br /> <img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-903\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.iwate-kenpokubus.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/kenpokubus/images/recruit/kyouiku_03.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"165\" /></p>\n<ul>\n<li>車内装置説明</li>\n<li>車両機器操作</li>\n<li>非常コック・非常扉・発煙筒・消火器・赤旗の使用方法</li>\n<li>車いすスロープ機器操作</li>\n<li>車両構造</li>\n<li>日常点検</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"article\">\n<p class=\"entry-title\">点呼講習</p>\n<p class=\"figure right\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-903\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.iwate-kenpokubus.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/kenpokubus/images/recruit/kyouiku_04.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"165\" /><br /> <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-903\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.iwate-kenpokubus.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/kenpokubus/images/recruit/kyouiku_05.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"165\" /></p>\n<ul>\n<li>対面点呼の演習</li>\n<li>アルコールチェッカー</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"article end\">\n<p class=\"entry-title\">実技訓練</p>\n<p class=\"figure right\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-903\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.iwate-kenpokubus.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/kenpokubus/images/recruit/kyouiku_06.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"165\" /><br /> <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-903\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.iwate-kenpokubus.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/kenpokubus/images/recruit/kyouiku_07.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"165\" /></p>\n<ul>\n<li>乗務の手順（出勤・休憩・運転中・退勤）</li>\n<li>基本走行訓練　構内<br /> 内輪差、オーバーハング、車庫入れなど車両感覚の習得</li>\n<li>基本走行訓練　路上<br /> ドア開閉時や発進時、交差点通過等の安全確認の励行<br /> 車内案内、バス停の停車位置など</li>\n<li>日常点検、洗車、軽整備、整備手入</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"btn-app\"><a href=\"https://www.iwate-kenpokubus.co.jp/wp/recruit/form/\"><img decoding=\"async\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.iwate-kenpokubus.co.jp/wp/wp-content/themes/kenpokubus/images/recruit/btn_app.gif\" /></a></div>\n<ul id=\"recruit-sub-btn\">\n<li><a href=\"https://www.iwate-kenpokubus.co.jp/archives/1477/\" target=\"_blank\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\" alignnone\" src=\"https://www.iwate-kenpokubus.co.jp/wp/wp-admin/images/recruit_bt01.gif\" alt=\"バス運転士募集要項\" /></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.iwate-kenpokubus.co.jp/wp/recruit/flow/\" target=\"_blank\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.iwate-kenpokubus.co.jp/wp/wp-admin/images/recruit_bt02.gif\" alt=\"運転士までの道のり\" /></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.iwate-kenpokubus.co.jp/wp/recruit/education/\" target=\"_blank\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.iwate-kenpokubus.co.jp/wp/wp-admin/images/recruit_bt03.gif\" alt=\"教育・研修制度\" /></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.iwate-kenpokubus.co.jp/wp/recruit/message/\" target=\"_blank\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.iwate-kenpokubus.co.jp/wp/wp-admin/images/recruit_bt04.gif\" alt=\"先輩からのメッセージ\" /></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.iwate-kenpokubus.co.jp/wp/voice/\" target=\"_blank\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.iwate-kenpokubus.co.jp/wp/wp-admin/images/recruit_bt05.gif\" alt=\"お客様からの声\" /></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>